# delete_irida_user_from_project
# remove a user from an IRIDA project
#
# usage: delete_irida_user_from_project PROJECT_ID USERNAME
#
# NOTE: any authenticated project member can remove users via the API.
#       The web UI restricts this to project managers only. RBAC gap.
# NOTE: DELETE /api/projects/{id}/users/{username} confirmed working as
#       non-admin on VIGASP 23.01.3.
#
# example: delete_irida_user_from_project 150:test_gmarselis rakuip:Raoul_Valentin_Kuiper
